🧩 Why This Is Actually Powerful

You’re merging 3 things:
	1.	Computer Vision → understands what you’re looking at
	2.	Instruction Graphs (manuals) → structured steps
	3.	Context Awareness → knows what step you’re currently on

That’s HUGE because manuals are:
	•	Linear (Step 1 → Step 10)
	•	But reality is non-linear (people jump, mess up, skip steps)

This system turns manuals into:

State machines that adapt to what you actually did

